  (text "Note 1. Assuming 2.7V max output from the OPA380: \nMax Iout from Photodiodes: 480uF, 160uF, 40uF.\nMaximum corresponding reference resistors: 5.6 kΩ, 16.9 kΩ, 67.5 kΩ\nNote 2. All \"*External ...\" blocks are parts of the Homebase schematic\nthat do not appear on the Homebase PCB, but on another PCB within the \nHomebase." 
